Privacy Policy – Gravity Flip - Platform Jumper

Effective Date: 29th August 2025

Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how Gravity Flip – Platform Jumper (“we,” “our,” or “the App”) handles user information.

1. Information We Collect

No Personal Data: We do not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information (such as name, email, phone number).

Non-Personal Data (for analytics & ads):

Device information (e.g., model, OS version).

Usage data (e.g., gameplay sessions, score statistics).

Advertising identifiers (to show relevant ads).

This information is collected automatically by third-party services integrated into the game (like Google Play Services, AdMob, or analytics tools).

2. How We Use Information

We may use the collected non-personal data to:

Improve gameplay experience and performance.

Show relevant ads and reward-based ads.

Analyze crashes, bugs, and app usage for improvements.

3. Third-Party Services

The game may use trusted third-party SDKs or services, including but not limited to:

Google Play Services (leaderboards, achievements, cloud saves).

AdMob / Ad Partners (to display ads).

Analytics Tools (to understand usage and improve the game).

These services may collect and use information in accordance with their own privacy policies.

4. Children’s Privacy

Our game is suitable for a general audience. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal data, please contact us so we can remove it.

5. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your data, but please note that no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure.

6. Your Choices

You can disable personalized ads in your device settings (Google > Ads > Opt out of Ads Personalization).

You may uninstall the game at any time to stop data collection.

7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected in this page with an updated effective date.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:
